    Created by IntelliJ IDEA. User: pereira Date: Jun 18, 2005 Time: 9:11:24 PM

    Binary heap implementation of PriorityQueue. Based on algorithm in Corman, Leiserson, Rivest, and Stein (Section 6.5).
